casebody.data:
First Department,

September, 1940.

(September 27, 1940.) Charles Mortimer Miller, Respondent, v. Madison Square Garden Corporation, Appellant.

Order unanimously reversed, with twenty dollars costs and disbursements, and motion denied. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., O’Malley, Townley, Glennon and Untermyer, JJ.
